    "causal_summary": "Operator identified the cloud-reranker auto-routing footgun: VOYAGE_API_KEY and COHERE_API_KEY were being treated as cross-encoder activation signals AND as auto-routing triggers in resolveProvider(). Since Voyage sells both embeddings AND reranking under the same key, an operator setting VOYAGE_API_KEY for embeddings would unintentionally also activate Voyage reranking. This packet removes the cloud paths entirely: RerankerProvider type narrowed to 'local'; PROVIDER_CONFIG voyage/cohere entries + rerankVoyage()/rerankCohere() functions deleted; hasAnyCrossEncoderOptInSignal() no longer auto-enables on API-key presence. Post-013 activation requires explicit SPECKIT_CROSS_ENCODER=true + RERANKER_LOCAL=true. 8 files modified, 1 test file deleted, ~340 net LOC removed, 31/31 tests pass.",
